version_description: So this tab would be for those who want to see the way to play the "transposed 2" chords in their standard tuning shape instead of in the DGCFAD tuning shape.
There are two other versions of this song. One is not in Standard (Ver 1), one is incorrect (Ver 2) and one requires a Capo. My version is Standard, without a capo, and correct.

This is essentially a fixed version 2, except the chords progress the whole way and is on Capo 3. What makes this version special is that it leverages standard tuning which makes including this song in a long playlist easier since you don't need to change the tuning of your guitar to play it.
This version is complete, it has all the chords, including the change of tone at the last parts of the song. Enjoy.
